publisher			Wadjet Eye Games							
publish_time	 2014年4月24日		
desc_long							评测						“It’s pretty much the perfect ending, both wrapping up and nailing a series that’s been going from strength to strength since it first appeared way back in 2006.”Rock Paper Shotgun“The stakes are immense this time around. Rosa and Joey deal with more difficult cases and emotions than they’ve previously had to tackle. The game seems to be the longest yet and features a wide variety of locations to explore and characters to meet.”Hardcore Gamer“Its strong storytelling and solid puzzles will win you over.”Adventure Gamers												关于这款游戏							A dead man’s soul cries out against the force of a ferocious blizzard. He cries for help. He cries for answers. Then he screams as he is torn apart like damp tissue paper.This wasn’t the first time, and it won’t be the last.The police are powerless to stop it, so the duty falls to the only ones who can. What force could be so powerful – and so malevolent – that it would destroy the very core of a life in order to get what it wants? Rosa Blackwell and Joey Mallone mean to find out, even if it means risking themselves in the process.						
title	 Blackwell Epiphany			
